%20Council%20should%20be%20India's%20right%20in%20this%20changed%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20changing%20these%20institutions%20would%20take%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20said%20it%20was%20good%20to%20see%20India%20take%20its%20place%20in%20institutions%20like%20the%20Quad%20and%20the%20G20.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20G7%20regularly%20invites%20India%20to%20attend%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20standing%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729490700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ffkrrv3uo_david-cameron-_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-needs-permanent-seat-at-un-security-council-david-cameron-at-ndtv-world-summit-6836795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20needs%20India's%20perspective%20on%20the%20challenges%20it%20faces%20and%20the%20country%20should%20get%20a%20permanent%20seat%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%2C%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20David%20Cameron%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Live%20Updates%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Speaks%20At%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20On%20'The%20India%20Century'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENDTV%20proudly%20presents%20its%20flagship%20event%2C%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%202024%20-%20The%20India%20Century%2C%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20at%20the%20inaugural%20session%20-%20The%20India%20Century.%20In%20his%20keynote%20address%2C%20PM%20Modi%20spoke%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-excited-about-indias-growth-investment-pm-narendra-modi-at-ndtv-world-summit-6836905%5C%22%3Eabout%20why%20the%2021st%20Century%20is%20'The%20India%20Century'%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20the%20country%20is%20growing%20rapidly%20and%20how%20investors%2