-cry-wolf-trailer-1236183953%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Netflix%20Documentary%20Shows%20London%20Woman's%209-Year%20Catfishing%20Nightmare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKirat%20Assi%2C%20a%20London%20resident%20and%20radio%20presenter%2C%20thought%20she%20was%20finally%20going%20to%20meet%20the%20man%20she'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20with.%20They%20had%20texted%20each%20other%20for%20nine%20years.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20two%20came%20face-to-face%2C%20Ms%20Assi%20found%20someone%20she%20never%20expected.%20In%20a%20shocking%20twist%2C%20her%20entire%20relationship%20had%20been%20an%20elaborate%20catfishing%20scheme%2C%20orchestrated%20not%20by%20a%20stranger%20but%20by%20someone%20much%20closer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20female%20cousin%2C%20Simran.%20Now%2C%20Netflix%20has%20released%20a%20documentary%2C%20%3Cem%3ESweet%20Bobby%3A%20My%20Catfish%20Nightmare%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20retelling%20this%20story%20of%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20in%202009%20when%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0got%20a%20friend%20request%20from%20%E2%80%98Bobby%2C'%20a%20supposed%20cardiologist%20from%20west%20London.%20Soon%2C%20it%20evolved%20into%20a%20long-distance%20relationship.%20The%20two%20shared%20connections%20within%20their%20Sikh%20community%2C%20which%20made%20the%20relationship%20seem%20genuine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20their%20online%20conversations%20deepened%2C%20but%20as%20years%20passed%2C%20their%20connection%20remained%20virtual%2C%20with%20Bobby%20continually%20giving%20bizarre%20reasons%20for%20why%20they%20couldn't%20meet%20in%20person.%20The%20excuses%20were%20nothing%20short%20of%20dramatic%20%E2%80%94%20claims%20of%20being%20shot%2C%20suffering%20a%20stroke%20and%20even%20entering%20witness%20protection%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20m3g1kdpvo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20what%20made%20these%20lies%20convincing%20to%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0were%20the%20people%20she%20believed%20were%20corroborating%20his%20stories.%20They%20were%20always%20someone%20close%20to%20Bobby%2C%20or%20that's%20what%20she%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nine%20years%20of%20emotional%20manipulation%2C%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0finally%20confronted%20the%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20this%20entire%20thing%20was%20a%20hoax%2C%20and%20the%20man%20she%20thought%20she%20was%20in%20love%20with%20didn't%20even%20exist.%20She%20had%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20catfishing%20scheme%20and%20the%20person%20behind%20the%20messages%20wasn't%20Bobby%20but%20her%20female%20cousin%2C%20Simran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20in%20Birmingham%20Live%2C%20throughout%20the%20ordeal%2C%20Ms%20Assi%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20leaned%20on%20Simran%20for%20support.%20However%2C%20one%20day%2C%20Simran%20dropped%20the%20bombshell%2C%20revealing%20to%20a%20devastated%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0that%20she%20hadn't%20been%20communicating%20with%20Bobby%20all%20along%20%E2%80%94%20she%20had%20been%20speaking%20to%20Simran%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20left%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0devastated%20and%20questioning%20her%20judgement.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20could%20you%20have%20been%20so%20stupid%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects%20now%2C%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20m3g1kdpvo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirat%20Assi's%20experience%20was%20first%20shared%20in%20a%20popular%202021%20podcast%20by%20Tortoise%2C%20but%20the%20story%20has%20since%20gained%20renewed%20attention%20with%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Netflix%20documentary%2C%20Sweet%20Bobby%3A%20My%20Catfish%20Nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Assi%20says%20she%20has%20faced%20criticism%20and%20questions%2C%20with%20many%20asking%20how%20she%20could%20fall%20for%20such%20a%20scheme.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20people%20who%20might%20still%20think%20I'm%20stupid%2C%20that's%20fine%2C%20you're%20allowed%20your%20opinion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20BBC%20Asian%20Network%20News%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20not%20stupid%2C%20I'm%20not%20dumb.%20I'm%20the%20one%20that's%20chosen%20to%20speak.%20I'm%20the%20one%20that's%20put%20myself%20out%20in%20the%20firing%20line%20and%20I%20hope%20others%20will%20come%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Assi%20feels%20it%20was%20important%20to%20publicly%20tell%20her%20story%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20stigmas%20surrounding%20such%20issues%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20community%20in%20the%20UK.%20Explaining%20how%20the%20fear%20of%20judgement%20often%20silences%20victims%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20so%20scared%20to%20open%20up%20about%20these%20issues.%20Because%20of%20how%20a%20community%20will%20be%20seen%20by%20wider%20society%2C%20the%20victims%20in%20our%20communities%20keep%20suffering.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reluctance%20to%20address%20uncomfortable%20topics%20was%20evident%20even%20in%20her%20own%20family.%20Speaking%20of%20her%20father's%20experience%20with%20the%20situation%2C%20Kirat%20Assi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20doesn't%20want%20to%20know%20what%20happened.%20Because%20to%20face%20up%20to%20what%20happened%2C%20and%20how%20horrific%20it%20was%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20painful.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20traumatic%20experience%2C%20Kirat%20Assi%20remains%20open%20to%20having%20conversations%20about%20her%20experience%2C%20encouraging%20people%20to%20approach%20her%20if%20they%20have%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%2C%20however%2C%20has%20not%20faced%20criminal%20charges%20for%20the%20catfishing%2C%20but%20Ms%20Assi%20took%20civil%20action%20against%20her%2C%20resulting%20in%20compensation%20and%20an%20apology.%20In%20the%20Netflix%20documentary%2C%20a%20statement%20from%20Simran%20was%20included%20where%20she%20said%20she%20views%20the%20situation%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20rejecting%20the%20accusations%20made%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Kirat%20Assi%20has%20sought%20closure%2C%20she%20says%20the%20motivation%20behind%20Simran's%20deceit%20remains%20a%20mystery.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20I've%20long%20given%20up.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20that%20person%20went%2C%20you%20can't%20ever%20justify%20it.%20I%20can't%20understand%20why%20you%20didn't%20stop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Assi%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20she%20is%20determined%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20rebuilding%20her%20life%20and%20even%20starting%20to%20date%20again.%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20going%20to%20carry%20on%20working%20towards%20goals%20and%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729487220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0f2eaqp_sweet-bobby-netflix-documentary_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsweet-bobby-new-netflix-documentary-shows-london-womans-9-year-catfishing-nightmare-6836568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kirat%20Assi%2C%20a%20London%20resident%20and%20radio%20presenter%2C%20thought%20she%20was%20finally%20going%20to%20meet%20the%20man%20she'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20with.%20They%20had%20texted%20each%20other%20for%20nine%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia%20On%20Path%20Of%20Unprecedented%20Growth%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Top%20Quotes%20At%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20discussions%20in%20the%20last%20four%20or%20five%20years%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20common%3A%20tension%20about%20the%20future.%20During%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%2C%20there%20was%20stress%20over%20economy%2C%20unemployment%2C%20and%20health%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20India%2C%20we%20are%20discussing%20the%20'India%20Century'.%20India%20is%20the%20ray%20of%20hope%20amid%20global%20crisis.%20India%20giving%20hope%20to%20the%20world%20engulfed%20in%20various%20concerns%2C%20it%20is%20working%20on%20unprecedented%20scale%20and%20speed%20in%20every%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20challenges%20in%20front%20of%20India%20but%20we%20are%20feeling%20a%20sense%20of%20positivity%20here%20and%20that%20is%20why%20we%20are%20discussing%20the%20'India%20Century'.%20India's%20speed%20and%20scale%20are%20unprecedented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20completed%20125%20days%20of%20our%20term.%20Around%203%20crore%20new%20homes%20for%20the%20poor%20were%20built%2C%20infra%20projects%20worth%20Rs%209%20lakh%20crore%20infrastructure%20projects%20have%20started%2C%2015%20new%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20are%20running%2C%208%20new%20airports%20are%20in%20operation%2C%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore%20package%20for%20youth%20have%20announced%2C%205%20lakh%20health%20insurance%20for%20those%20above%2070%20-%20all%20of%20these%20things%20happened%20in%20just%20125%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeveral%20agencies%20have%20revised%20upward%20India's%20growth%20forecast%20due%20to%20speed%20of%20work%20in%20our%20third%20term.%20In%20125%20days%2C%20we%20have%20approved%2012%20new%20industrial%20dots.%20BSE%20Indices%20have%20grown%20by%207%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia's%20list%20of%20achievements%20is%20long%20and%20I%20am%20just%20discussing%20the%20first%20125%20days%20of%20our%20third%20term.%20The%20world%20has%20come%20to%20India%20to%20discuss%20various%20issues%20in%20the%20first%20125%20days.%20This%20shows%20India's%20vision%20and%20hope%20and%20these%20issues%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20lot%20is%20happening%20in%20India.%20India%20has%20picked%20up%20the%20pace%20of%20growth%20in%20our%20third%20term.%20Our%20government%20is%20taking%20quick%20decisions%20and%20making%20reforms.%20I%20meet%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20my%20public%20life%20who%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20working%20so%20hard%3F%20India%20is%20doing%20well.%26quot%3B%20But%20my%20answer%20is%20always%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20dreams%20and%20goals%20that%20we%20have%2C%20we%20can't%20be%20at%20rest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%2012%20crore%20toilets%20have%20been%20built%2C%20and%2016%20crore%20homes%20have%20gas%20connections.%20Is%20it%20enough%3F%20My%20answer%20is%20no.%20This%20is%20not%20enough.%20India%20is%20a%20country%20with%20a%20young%20population%20and%20we%20have%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20country.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20India's%20vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20tradition%20that%20every%20government%20compares%20its%20work%20with%20the%20previous%20one.%20We%20used%20to%20walk%20this%20path%20but%20from%20now%20on%20we%20can't%20compare%20the%20past%20and%20present%20and%20be%20happy%20with%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20metric%20of%20success%20from%20now%20on%20would%20be%20'What%20we%20want%20to%20achieve'%20-%20India%20has%20a%20forward-looking%20approach.%20A%20vision%20for%20a%20developed%20India%20by%202047%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mindset.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E140%20Crore%20people%20are%20driving%20the%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20vision.%20When%20the%20government%20started%20working%20on%20the%20idea%2C%20lakhs%20of%20people%20gave%20their%20suggestions%2C%20and%20based%20on%20that%2C%20India%20made%20its%20goals%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20era%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20and%20the%20future%20of%20the%20world%20is%20linked%20with%20AI.%20For%20the%20world%2C%20AI%20is%20artificial%20intelligence%20but%20for%20India%2C%20it%20is%20Aspirational%20India.%20India%20has%20started%20the%20AI%20m%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729487160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2