C%20auto%20cos%20drag%20Sensex%2C%20Nifty%20into%20red%3B%20Kotak%20Bank%20down%204%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729484021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-today-sensex-nifty-nse-bse-hdfc-bank-waaree-energies-ipo-124102100048_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20Today%3A%20Markets%20in%20India%20opened%20higher%20on%20Monday%2C%20tracking%20Friday's%20gains%20on%20Wall%20Street%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-today-sensex-nifty-nse-bse-hdfc-bank-waaree-energies-ipo-124102100048_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Cops%20Seek%20Telegram%20Info%20On%20'Justice%20League%20India'%20After%20Rohini%20Blast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20an%20explosion%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Rohini%20set%20off%20a%20multi-agency%20investigation%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20written%20to%20authorities%20in%20the%20Telegram%20app%2C%20seeking%20information%20about%20a%20handle%20named%20'Justice%20League%20India'%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20evening%2C%20the%20Telegram%20handle%20posted%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20blast%20and%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20it.%20According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20they%20have%20yet%20to%20receive%20a%20response%20from%20Telegram%20to%20their%20query.%20No%20known%20terror%20organisation's%20name%20has%20emerged%20in%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20blast%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%207.47%20am%20yesterday%2C%20a%20loud%20blast%20damaged%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20CRPF%20school%20in%20Rohini's%20Prashant%20Vihar%20area.%20While%20no%20one%20was%20injured%2C%20the%20explosion%20shattered%20windows%20of%20cars%20parked%20near%20the%20school%20and%20hoardings%20of%20shops%20in%20the%20area.%20A%20cloud%20of%20smoke%20was%20seen%20billowing%20after%20the%20blast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20police%20reached%20the%20spot.%20Fire%20engines%20and%20a%20bomb%20squad%20were%20called%20in.%20Later%2C%20sniffer%20dogs%20were%20pressed%20into%20action%20to%20look%20for%20clues.%20A%20forensic%20team%20examined%20the%20spot%20and%20collected%20samples%2C%20including%20a%20white%20powder-like%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-terror%20probe%20body%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Guard%20joined%20the%20investigation%20too.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20Explosives%20Act%20and%20the%20area%20has%20been%20cordoned%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%2C%20police%20sources%20said%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20a%20crude%20bomb.%20Police%20are%20scanning%20CCTV%20footage%20in%20the%20area%20to%20identify%20who%20planted%20it.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20police%20are%20not%20ruling%20out%20a%20conspiracy%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explosion%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20triggered%20a%20political%20blame%20game.%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20targeted%20the%20Centre%2C%20which%20controls%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%20the%20blast%20had%20exposed%20Delhi's%20%26quot%3Bcrumbling%26quot%3B%20law%20and%20order%20system.%20%26quot%3BThe%20responsibility%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Delhi%20is%20with%20BJP's%20central%20government.%20But%20BJP%20ignores%20this%20and%20uses%20its%20time%20to%20disrupt%20the%20work%20of%20Delhi's%20elected%20governments.%20This%20is%20why%20Delhi's%20situation%20is%20now%20that%20of%20Mumbai%20during%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Underworld.%20Bullets%20are%20being%20fired%20in%20the%20open%2C%20gangsters%20are%20extorting%20money%20and%20criminals%20are%20upbeat.%20The%20BJP%20neither%20has%20the%20intent%20nor%20the%20ability%20(to%20handle%20this)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20by%20mistake%2C%20Delhiites%20give%20them%20(BJP)%20charge%20of%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20hospitals%2C%20power%20and%20water%20supply%20will%20become%20the%20same%20as%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20BJP's%20Shazia%20Ilmi%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20puppet%20CM%20is%20known%20for%20this.%20If%20you%20make%20her%20speak%20on%20any%20topic%2C%20it%20is%20always%20about%20the%20Centre.%20Something%20very%20serious%20has%20happened.%20The%20situation%20is%20totally%20in%20control.%20Instead%20of%20expressing%20anxiety%20about%20the%20situation%20and%20(thinking)%20what%20should%20be%20done%2C%20a%20political%20blame%20game%20has%20begun.%20It%20is%20immature%20and%20irresponsible%20to%20always%20do%20politics%20on%20serious%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20in%20Delhi%20are%20due%20in%20February%20and%20AAP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2010%20years%20now%2C%20is%20pushing%20hard%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20now%20out%20on%20bail%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%2C%20stepped%20down%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20last%20month%20and%20said%20he%20would%20return%20to%20the%20top%20office%20only%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B%20elects%20him%20again.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20Atishi%20took%20over%20the%20job%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729483920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fb3t2e4qo_rohini-blast_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-cops-seek-telegram-info-on-justice-league-india-after-rohini-blast-6836359%22%2C%22summary%2