0personal%20comforts%20in%20a%20fully-stocked%20bunker%20under%20the%20ravaged%20city%20of%20Khan%20Younis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20shared%20video%20footage%20that%20details%20the%20inside%20of%20Sinwar's%20underground%20hideout.%20The%20video%20shows%20a%20well-equipped%20bunker%2C%20complete%20with%20modern%20showers%2C%20several%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20fully%20functional%20kitchen%2C%20stocked%20with%20food%20rations%20labelled%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Palestinian%20Refugee%20Agency%20(UNRWA)%20logo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%2061%2C%20had%20taken%20refuge%20in%20the%20bunker%20with%20his%20guards%20and%20close%20associates%20as%20the%20war%20above%20ground%20escalated.%20The%20footage%20shows%20a%20bag%20of%20UNRWA-supplied%20food%2C%20reinforcing%20Israel's%20longstanding%20accusation%20that%20Hamas%20steals%20from%20international%20agencies%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20already%20dire%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20IDF%20has%20released%20footage%20showing%20their%20entry%20into%20Sinwar's%20bunker%2C%20where%20UNWRA%20bags%20and%20millions%20of%20shekels%20were%20found.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSinwar%20and%20other%20Hamas%20leaders%20have%20been%20siphoning%20billions%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20allegedly%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNWRA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNWRA%3C%2Fa%3E's%20involvement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZRcr5UWKmF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZRcr5UWKmF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20David%20Saranga%20(%40DavidSaranga)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDavidSaranga%2Fstatus%2F1847915812285284355%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bunker%20cont