remembered%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20Vietnam%20back%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20nine%20days%2C%20but%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2019%2C%202023%2C%20Jones%20retired%20from%20law%20enforcement%20after%2026%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20month%20later%2C%20he%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20his%20wife%20packed%20up%20their%20lives%2C%20sold%20their%20house%2C%20and%20left%20Lake%20County%2C%20Florida%2C%20to%20embark%20on%20their%20next%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourist-mistakes-thailand-chiang-mai-guide-list-holiday-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChiang%20Mai%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20province%20in%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20sight%20unseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c673279f-70e7-42fd-987f-753ef6f8192e%5C%22%3EMoving%20halfway%20around%20the%20globe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChiang%20Mai%20is%20about%20450%20miles%20north%20of%20Bangkok.%20It%20has%20long%20been%20a%20popular%20destination%20for%20tourists%20and%20expats%20alike%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20stunning%20ancient%20temples%2C%20bustling%20markets%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-cities-for-digital-nomad-remote-work-move-live-abroad-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelatively%20low%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20says%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20there%20after%20doing%20his%20research%20and%20speaking%20to%20people%20he%20met%20on%20expat%20Facebook%20groups%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e2f9c6ac7b701e7cafd06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20a%20house%20with%20a%20large%20yard%20for%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20hard%20enough%2C%20there's%20a%20road%20map%20out%20there%20for%20you%20to%20follow%20and%20adjust%20accordingly%20to%20what%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20being%20a%20cop%20has%20prepared%20him%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20unknown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20he%20chose%20Chiang%20Mai%20was%20because%20he%20enjoyed%20northern%20Thai%20cuisine%20and%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20a%20place%20that%20was%20quiet%20but%20still%20easily%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20go%20somewhere%20where%20I%20didn't%20have%20all%20the%20noise%20of%20a%20city%2C%20but%20I%20had%20the%20conveniences%20right%20up%20the%20road%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20decided%20to%20rent%20instead%20of%20buying%20a%20house.%20To%20him%2C%20it%20didn't%20make%20sense%20to%20purchase%20property%20in%20a%20new%20country%20without%20familiarizing%20himself%20with%20the%20different%20areas%20where%20he%20could%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sofa%20in%20the%20office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670cb4f63f2165d716e0886d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInstead%20of%20buying%20a%20place%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20rent%20instead.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%20with%20you%2C%20we'll%20probably%20rent%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20lives%20unless%20we%20find%20a%20special%20place%20that%20we%20want%20to%20call%20our%20home%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Jones%20and%20his%20wife%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jet-vacation-japan-toy-poodle-dog-expensive-holiday-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C