ner.%20There%20was%20music%20playing%2C%20and%20we%20both%20found%20ourselves%20walking%20to%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20dance%20floor%20to%20introduce%20ourselves.%20We%20talked%20for%2015%20minutes%20and%20then%20decided%20to%20hang%20out%20that%20night.%20We%20had%20a%20very%20instant%20connection.%20I%20remember%20after%20we%20hung%20out%2C%20his%20friend%20asked%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20you%20tell%20me%20about%20your%20girlfriend%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20because%20I%20just%20met%20her%2015%20minutes%20ago.%26quot%3B%20As%20clich%C3%A9%20as%20it%20sounds%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20we'd%20known%20each%20other%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4e19f90-626e-4464-9013-c7a7b8557a7b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20brought%20up%20non-monogamy%20early%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20night%20after%20we%20met%20at%20Burning%20Man%2C%20I%20told%20Seth%20I%20was%20non-monogamous.%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20had%20friends%20who%20were%20non-monogamous%20and%20that%20I%20was%20curious%20about%20having%20an%20open%20relationship.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20could%20be%20open%20to%20an%20open%20relationship.%20When%20he%20said%20that%2C%20I%20thought%20he%20was%20saying%20he%20would%20also%20be%20open%20on%20his%20side%2C%20but%20he%20meant%20that%20he%20was%20open%20to%20figuring%20out%20how%20he%20could%20support%20me%20in%20doing%20what%20I%20want%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20his%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Burning%20Man%2C%20he%20headed%20home%20to%20San%20Francisco%20while%20I%20headed%20home%20to%20New%20York%2C%20but%20we%20stayed%20in%20touch.%20Two%20weeks%20later%2C%20he%20came%20to%20visit%20me%20in%20New%20York%2C%20and%20then%20two%20weeks%20after%20that%2C%20I%20went%20to%20visit%20him%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20We%20did%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-marriage-lessons-distance-doesnt-work-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elong-distance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20before%20Seth%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20in%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20a%20month%20into%20our%20long-distance%20relationship%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20his%20girlfriend.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20cute%20that%20he%20asked%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes.%26quot%3B%20I%20realized%20that%20for%20him%2C%20being%20his%20girlfriend%20meant%20being%20exclusive.%20So%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20this%20mean%20I%20can't%20have%20sex%20with%20other%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYep%2C%20that's%20what%20it%20means.%26quot%3B%20We%20discussed%20it%20further%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20ready%20for%20me%20to%20date%20other%20people%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20six%20months%20into%20the%20relationship%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20OK%20for%20me%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20other%20people%2C%20but%20only%20with%20people%20I'd%20already%20had%20sex%20with%20before%20I%20met%20him%2C%20only%20with%20people%20that%20had%20a%20partner%2C%20and%20only%20when%20he%20was%20away%20since%20we%20were%20long%20distance.%20A%20little%20over%20a%20year%20into%20the%20relationship%2C%20we%20got%20to%20my%20ideal%20stage%20of%20me%20being%20able%20to%20date%20whomever%20I%20wanted%20more%20regularly.%20For%20my%20dates%2C%20we%20started%20off%20with%20once%20a%20month%2C%20then%20once%20every%20couple%20of%20weeks.%20Now%20I%20have%20freedom%2C%20but%20we'll%20still%20have%20a%20conversation%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20went%20on%20a%20date%20with%20someone%20else%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20Seth%20was%20jealous%20and%20having%20a%20hard%20time.%20I%20would%20come%20home%20wanting%20to%20connect%20with%20him%20either%20because%20being%20with%20someone%20else%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20great%20Seth%20is%2C%20or%20I%20would%20have%20a%20very%20fun%20experience%2C%20sexually%20or%20otherwise%2C%20with%20my%20date%20and%20want%20to%20replicate%20that%20experience%20with%20him.%20But%20Seth%20found%20it%20strange%20that%20I'd%20want%20to%20connect%20with%20him%20after%20a%20date%20and%20would%20act%20a%20little%20distant%20at%20first.%20When%20we%20talked%20about%20it%2C%20he%20shared%20that%20it%20took%20him%20more%20time%20to%20shake%20off%20the%20feeling%20that%20I%20had%20just%20come%20back%20from%20a%20date%20with%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20a%20partial%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Ask%2C%20Don't%20Tell%26quot%3B%20system%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20my%20dates.%20While%20he%20knows%20I%20went%20on%20a%20date%2C%20I%20don't%20share%20details%20about%20the%20date%20and%20occasionally%2C%20I'll%20pretend%20like%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20knows%20the%20person%20I'm%20dating%2C%20he's%20always%20been%20open%20to%20allowing%20them%20over%20for%20an%20event%20or%20even%20attending%20an%20event%20where%20he%20knows%20they'll%20be%20there.%20I%20may%20not%20share%20much%20about%20my%20dates%2C%20but%20it's%20nice%20that%20he's%20open%20to%20meeting%20the%20people%20I%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2ca1765-66bc-4a4d-adc7-eed804cbdf02%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20partner%20has%20the%20option%20to%20be%20non%20monogamous%20if%20he%20wants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeth%20isn't%20interested%20in%20a%20romantic%20or%20sexual%20connection%20with%20anyone%20else%20and%20hasn't%20been%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%20but%20he%20has%20the%20option%20to%20do%20so%20if%20he%20ever%20wants%20to.%20While%20I%20feel%20recharged%20by%20being%20with%20other%20people%2C%20Seth%20is%20an%20introvert%20who%20feels%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoing-on-solo-trips-without-kids-parents-take-turns-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecharged%20by%20being%20on%20his%20own%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20think%20his%20introversion%20is%20why%20he's%20OK%20with%20our%20dynamic.%20When%20I%20come%20back%20from%20spending%20time%20with%20others%2C%20we%20both%20feel%20recharged%20and%20ready%20to%20reconnect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20decided%20to%20share%20our%20dynamic%20with%20my%20mom's%20side%20of%20the%20family.%20I'll%20tell%20my%20mom%20about%20a%20date%20I%20went%20on%2C%20and%20she'll%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20let%20Seth%20hear%20you.%26quot%3B%20I%20just%20tell%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BMom%2C%20it's%20OK%3B%20Seth%20knows.%26quot%3B%20My%20mom%20really%20likes%20Seth%20and%20doesn't%20want%20me%20to%20harm%20our%20relationship%20by%20seeing%20other%20people.%20I%20didn't%20tell%20my%20dad%20about%20the%20details%20of%20our%20connection%20until%20more%20recently%2C%20not%20out%20of%20fear%20or%20judgment%2C%20but%20because%20sex%20and%20relationships%20are%20not%20topics%20I'd%20ever%20previously%20spoken%20to%20him%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20I'm%20non-monogamous%2C%20there%20are%20temporary%20periods%2C%20usually%20about%20four%20months%2C%20when%20I'm%20monogamous.%20Being%20non-monogamous%20adds%20to%20my%20life%20the%20ability%20to%20feel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiological-reasons-youre-attracted-to-someone-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eattraction%20and%20connection%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20a%20person%20and%20pursue%20it.%20But%20attraction%20and%20connection%20with%20others%20don't%20always%20happen%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20my%20energy%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnever-date-again-prefer-drama-free-single-life-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethings%20other%20than%20dating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20close%20our%20relationship%20forever%20if%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20non-monogamy%20was%20no%20longer%20right%2C%20there's%20always%20an%20option%20for%20us%20to%20have%20a%20conversation%2C%20and%20if%20we%20had%20to%2C%20close%20it%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20an%20interesting%20personal%20story%20about%20your%20relationship%20or%20marriage%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acgriffin%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ecgriffin%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-partner-is-monogamous-but-im-not-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729454702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67129b9afd8ede6c99e3ffe0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-partner-is-monogamous-but-im-not-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fernanda%20Fabian%20is%20non-monogamous%20but%20her%20partner%20Seth%20is.%20This%20is%20how%20they%20make%20their%20relationship%20work%20for%20both%20of%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgriffin%40businessinsider.com%20(Cailey%20Griffin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A282%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-partner-is-monogamous-but-im-not-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Missing%20crew%20members%20found%20dead%20after%20fighter%20jet%20crash%20in%20Washington%20state%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729453883000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114404854%2Cimgsize-695044.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A