rump%20has%20sought%20to%20promote%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20an%20issue%20he%20used%20to%20his%20advantage%20when%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20the%20presumptive%20Democratic%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Biden%20exited%20the%20race%20in%20July%2C%20and%20Harris%20became%20the%20nominee%2C%20she%20quickly%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-us-economy-would-look-like-with-trump-biden-presidency-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20with%20Trump%20on%20the%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20succeeded%20in%20eroding%20his%20once%20huge%20advantage%20on%20the%20issue%20in%20key%20swing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Chicago%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-cosmc-bigger-burgers-mccripsy-expansion-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20largest%20fast-food%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20over%2040%2C000%20locations.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20major%20employer.%20In%20Pennsylvania%20alone%2C%20the%20company%20says%20its%20franchises%20employ%20over%2025%2C000%20people.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20BI%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20McDonald's%20location%20that%20Trump%20visited%20said%20he%20was%20honored%20to%20%26quot%3Bshowcase%26quot%3B%20the%20restaurant%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20small%2C%20independent%20business%20owner%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fundamental%20value%20of%20my%20organization%20that%20we%20proudly%20open%20our%20doors%20to%20everyone%20who%20visits%20the%20Feasterville%20community.%20That's%20why%20I%20accepted%20former%20President%20Trump's%20request%20to%20observe%20the%20transformative%20working%20experience%20that%201%20in%208%20Americans%20have%20had%3A%20a%20job%20at%20McDonald's%2C%26quot%3B%20Derek%20Giacomantonio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20former%20crew%20member%2C%20I%20can%20attest%20this%20job%20is%20more%20than%20burgers%20and%20fries%2C%20but%20a%20meaningful%20pathway%20to%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20appetite%20for%20McDonald's%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20fast%20food%20chains%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20well%20documented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20the%20requisite%20number%20of%20GOP%20delegates%20needed%20to%20secure%20the%20party's%202016%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBF4raEHmhag%2F%3Ftaken-by%3Drealdonaldtrump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20was%20photographed%3C%2Fa%3E%20eating%20a%20McDonald's%20Big%20Mac%20on%20his%20private%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20January%202019%2C%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-serves-fast-food-in-white-house-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehosted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20college%20championship-winning%20Clemson%20University%20football%20team%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20where%20he%20ordered%20an%20assortment%20of%20fast-food%20staples%20for%20the%20players%20from%20McDonald's%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20and%20Domino's%20Pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20campaigns%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-harris-mcdonalds-fry-cook-economy-election-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729448899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671552969b3250dbbce8a2ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-harris-mcdonalds-fry-cook-economy-election-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20claimed%20without%20evidence%20that%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20never%20worked%20at%20McDonald's%20during%20a%20summer%20in%20the%201980s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com