%20oasis%20for%20women%20in%20the%20slum%2C%20the%20fight%20to%20reclaim%20this%20space%20is%20constant%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20dealing%20with%20drunk%20men%20or%20young%20boys%20playing%20mobile%20games%20like%20PubG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20early%20on%20that%20aggression%20is%20not%20going%20to%20help.%20Personally%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20fight%20or%20flight%20scenario%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20very%20fight-oriented%20person%2C%20but%20I%20realise%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20scenario%20that%20will%20never%20work.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20go%20and%20sit%20very%20close%20to%20these%20men%20even%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20very%20drunk.%20I%E2%80%99d%20go%20sit%20next%20to%20them%20and%20that%20would%20make%20them%20uncomfortable.%20They%20would%20start%20moving%20away%20while%20I%20am%20also%20helping%20them%20understand%20why%20we%20have%20created%20these%20spaces.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20also%20agree%20to%20get%20a%20drink%2C%20go%20to%20these%20%E2%80%98shady%E2%80%99%20bars%2C%20sit%20and%20talk%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20they%20saw%20me%20as%20this%20%E2%80%98easy%20woman%E2%80%99%20but%20I%20held%20my%20ground.%20Looking%20at%20the%20greys%20(hair)%20on%20my%20head%2C%20these%20men%20had%20difficulty%20placing%20me.%20They%20would%20ask%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20are%20you%20doing%20here%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Are%20you%20starting%20a%20tailoring%20shop%20here%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20etc.%20They%20were%20also%20not%20comfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20space%20where%20women%20would%20do%20nothing.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20many%20men%20approach%20me%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Ask%20my%20wife%20to%20go%20home%20because%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%E2%80%99.%20My%20response%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98You%20can%20ask%20your%20wife%20directly%E2%80%99.%20I%20always%20encourage%20conversation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblo