ry%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devleena%20Chatterji%20(33).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20unites%20these%20two%20women%20is%20their%20struggle%20with%20endometriosis%20%E2%80%94%20a%20disease%20where%20tissue%20similar%20to%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20uterus%20grows%20outside%20of%20the%20uterus.%20Accompanied%20by%20debilitating%20pain%20every%20month%2C%20it%20made%20life%20difficult%20to%20function%20for%20these%20two.%20What%20was%20even%20more%20painful%20though%2C%20they%20share%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20doctor%20took%20them%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneha%20went%20to%20over%20seven%20doctors%20over%20five%20years%20in%20search%20of%20a%20solution%20or%20diagnosis%20for%20her%20pain.%20She%20was%20dismissed%20everywhere%20and%20sent%20with%20a%20prescription%20for%20painkillers.%20She%20suffered%20from%20excruciating%20pain%20ever%20since%20she%20first%20got%20her%20period%20at%2012.%20After%20enduring%20pain%20and%20not%20having%20a%20diagnosis%20for%20it%20for%2014%20years%2C%20she%20finally%20found%20a%20doctor%20who%20validated%20her%20pain%20and%20told%20her%20that%20it%20might%20be%20endometriosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cried%20that%20day.%20I%20finally%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20not%20in%20my%20head%2C%20and%20it%20was%20not%20because%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98low%20tolerance%20for%20pain%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sneha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevleena%20too%20found%20a%20solution%20after%20enduring%20pain%20for%20over%20two%20years.%20Like%20many%20women%2C%20she%20was%20repeatedly%20told%20by%20doctors%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20period%20pain%3B%20all%20women%20go%20through%20it.%20There%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20having%20in-laws%20who%20were%20doctors%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20blessing.%20Her%20mother-in-law%20believed%20her%20and%20helped%20guide%20her%20to%20the%20right%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20both%20women%20are%20raising%20awareness%20about%20this%20condition%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnotoriously%20difficult%20to%20diagnose%E2%80%9D.%20Endometriosis%20affects%20roughly%2010%20percent%20of%20women%20(over%20200%20million%20women)%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20anyone%20convince%20you%20that%20painkillers%20are%20the%20only%20solution.%20Your%20well-being%20is%20worth%20fighting%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devleena%2C%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Felt%20like%201%2C000%20needles%20were%20pricking%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250638%2Fahmedabad-jahnvi-trivedi-endometriosis-painful-menstruation-pain-awareness-menstrual-hygiene-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEndometriosis%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20disorder%20in%20which%20endometrial%20cells%20(inner%20lining%20of%20the%20uterus)%20grow%20outside%20the%20uterus%20and%20respond%20to%20ovarian%20hormones%2C%20thereby%20bleeding%20every%20month%20inside%20the%20abdomen%2C%20forming%20cysts%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vinoad%20Bharrati%2C%20obstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%2C%20Rising%20Medicare%20Hospital%2C%20and%20director%2C%20Elite%20Momz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Devleena%2C%20a%20research%20consultant%20with%20a%20PhD%20in%20organisational%20leadership%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20development%2C%20had%20experienced%20pain-free%20periods%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%20However%2C%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20began%20to%20suffer%20from%20sharp%20pains%20before%20her%20periods%2C%20leaving%20her%20unable%20to%20function%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerned%2C%20she%20spoke%20with%20her%20in-laws%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20doctors%2C%20and%20they%20connected%20her%20with%20a%20doctor%20friend.%20Initially%2C%20the%20doctor%20suspected%20appendicitis%20but%20also%20raised%20the%20possibility%20of%20endometriosis.%20He%20recommended%20an%20ultrasound%2C%20though%20diagnosing%20endometriosis%20is%20difficult%20and%20often%20requires%20surgery%20for%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20gold%20standard%20to%20diagnose%20endometriosis%20is%20a%20laparoscopy%2C%20a%20minimally%20invasive%20surgery%20in%20which%20conditions%20inside%20the%20abdomen%20can%20be%20seen.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20invasive%20mode%20of%20diagnosis.%20Clinical%20observation%20is%20crucial%20based%20on%20symptoms.%20Sonography%20and%20MRIs%20are%20important%20tools%20that%20aid%20in%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Vinoad%20Bharrati.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Devleena%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20ultrasound%20ruled%20out%20appendicitis%20initially.%20%E2%80%9CDoctors%20are%20hesitant%20to%20perform%20surgery%20just%20to%20check%20for%20endometriosis%20unless%20it%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20she%20was%20advised%20to%20adopt%20a%20wait-and-watch%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20pain%20returned%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20even%20more%20unbearable.%20While%20she%20was%20alone%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Devleena%20went%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%20at%20a%20hospital.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20ultrasound%20revealed%20that%20her%20appendix%20was%20swollen.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20doctors%20were%20confused%20because%20they%20thought%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20swollen%20enough%20to%20cause%20the%20kind%20of%20pain%20I%20was%20experiencing.%20They%20decided%20to%20do%20an%20appendectomy%20(removing%20the%20appendix)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother-in-law%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20surgeon%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20check%20for%20endometriosis%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20missed%20the%20endometriotic%20tissue%2C%20which%20was%20clearly%20visible%20in%20the%20ultrasound%2C%20misdiagnosing%20her%20with%20appendicitis%2C%20rues%20Devleena.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20surgery%2C%20they%20touched%20the%20endometriotic%20fluid%2C%20which%20led%20to%20it%20spreading%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20problems.%20I%20faced%20massive%20digestion%20issues%20over%20the%20next%20year%20and%20a%20half%20accompanied%20by%20painful%20periods%20due%20to%20the%20aspiration%20during%20the%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20led%20to%20her%20popping%20painkillers%20every%20eight%20hours%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368737%2Fpriyatama-sharma-child-sexual-abuse-survivor-education-women-educate-your-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20her%20pain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Just%20listen%20to%20us%3B%20we%20know%20our%20body%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20Sneha%2C%20a%20biologist%20turned%20science%20journalist%2C%20faced%20painful%20periods%20ever%20since%20she%20got%20her%20periods%20at%2012.%20The%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20her%20periods%20were%20horrible%20for%20her%20and%20affected%20her%20life.%20She%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20home%20from%20school%20sometimes%20as%20the%20pain%20was%20unmanageable.%20As%20she%20progressed%20to%20college%2C%20it%20led%20to%20her%20missing%20a%20few%20days%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20something%20called%20endometriosis%20existed%2C%20leading%20to%20her%20just%20living%20with%20it.%20She%20first%20visited%20a%20doctor%20when%20she%20was%2018%2C%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20take%20painkillers%20to%20manage%20the%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20assumption%20was%20always%20that%20I%20had%20a%20low%20pain%20tolerance.%20It%20was%20very%20frustrating%20as%20no%20one%20took%20me%20seriously.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20I%20really%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20endure%20the%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20working%20as%20a%20research%20fellow%2C%20she%20had%20to%20plan%20her%20work%20around%20this%20pain.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20work%20for%20three%20weeks%20every%20month%20as%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stand%20in%20the%20lab%20for%20a%20long%20time%20before%20my%20periods.%20I%20scheduled%20lighter%20work%20during%20the%20last%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-500x561.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sneha%20Khedkar%20went%20to%20over%20seven%20doctors%20over%20five%20years%20in%20search%20of%20a%20solution%20or%20diagnosis%20for%20her%20pain.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-500x561.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-768x862.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-1368x1536.jpeg%201368w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-07-at-11.01.41-min-min-1728552075-150x168.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m