20like%20the%20world%20was%20closing%20in%20on%20me%2C%20and%20my%20vision%20was%20beginning%20to%20blur%20when%20I%20was%20on%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rama%20explains.%20This%20anxiety%20led%20her%20to%20consult%20multiple%20ENT%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20asking%20the%20doctor%20for%20medication%20to%20make%20me%20feel%20better.%20Finally%2C%20one%20fine%20day%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20my%20ear.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20really%20think%20you%20have%20anxiety%20and%20should%20visit%20a%20psychiatrist%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20psychiatrist%20was%20an%20eye-opener.%20As%20she%20discussed%20her%20symptoms%2C%20the%20psychiatrist%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20generalised%20anxiety%20disorder.%20What%20troubled%20her%20the%20most%20was%20that%20as%20a%20journalist%20who%20had%20covered%20and%20commissioned%20several%20health%20stories%2C%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20recognised%20her%20own%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20I%20notice%20the%20signs%3F%20I%20realised%20we%20get%20so%20caught%20up%20in%20work.%20Newsrooms%20are%20chaotic%2C%20deadlines%20are%20relentless%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20think%20about%20our%20health.%20Even%20when%20we%20rest%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20still%20working.%20I%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20rest.%20Rest%2C%20to%20me%2C%20meant%20anxiety%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20doing%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Slow%20down%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20a%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20future%2C%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20her%20to%20sleep.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feared%20failure%20and%20not%20being%20able%20to%20achieve%20my%20goals.%20I%20had%20cold%20feet%20and%20palpitations.%20Fear%20had%20invaded%20my%20body.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20psychiatrist%20gave%20her%20some%20pills%20to%20begin%20her%20treatment.%20Rama%20also%20called%20her%20mother%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20support%20while%20her%20husband%20was%20at%20work.%20She%20stayed%20with%20her%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20providing%20unwavering%20support%20every%20time%20Rama%20broke%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20her%20mother%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20listened.%20They%20would%20go%20on%20long%20walks%2C%20sometimes%20lasting%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20which%20helped%20Rama%20get%20fresh%20air%2C%20sunlight%2C%20and%20a%20much-needed%20distraction%20from%20her%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20notes%20that%20while%20loved%20ones%20may%20not%20fully%20understand%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20they%20can%20still%20help.%20Over%20time%2C%20her%20husband%20became%20more%20receptive%20to%20her%20needs%20and%20worked%20alongside%20her%20to%20help%20her%20feel%20better.%20%E2%80%9CI%20recognise%20that%20I%20am%20privileged%20to%20have%20family%20and%20friends%20who%20have%20been%20a%20solid%20support%20system.%20Unfortunately%2C%20not%20everyone%20has%20this%20kind%20of%20access%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20expect%20your%20family%20to%20understand%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20going%20through%20right%20away.%20It%20takes%20time.%20The%20major%20thing%20people%20need%20to%20realise%20is%20that%20people%20with%20anxiety%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20advice%20or%20solutions.%20We%20just%20want%20to%20be%20heard.%20We%20can%20find%20our%