ovides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%20one-stop%20centres.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20runs%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20and%20provides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%20one-stop%20centres.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Break%20the%20intergenerational%20cycle%20of%20crime%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20says%20that%20whatever%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20spouse%20should%20not%20resort%20to%20heinous%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20acceptable%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20home%20is%20a%20place%20where%20you%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20loved%20and%20cared%20for.%20Children%20in%20such%20families%20are%20also%20affected%20as%20they%20are%20silent%20witnesses%20to%20the%20crime.%20Growing%20up%2C%20they%20assume%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20normal%20life%20is%20about.%20When%20such%20kids%20date%20or%20are%20in%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20they%20express%20love%20and%20anger%20in%20ways%20they%20learn%20from%20their%20own%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C